depositTokenCP(uint256,uint256).details: Burn tokens from existing CP holder

individualCPdata(address,uint256).details: Check balace of individual CPs - used by tax contract

interestClaim(uint256).details: Claim interest earned by the CP holder.

isOwner().details: Returns true if the caller is the current owner.

liquidateCP(address,uint256).details: Liquidate existing CP if rate < 150% - discount for liquidator rest to original holder.      If ETH is insufficient for the liquidation then the rest of the tokens will be reegistered       in the removal fund. For later removal - possible by ETH fee on token transfers.

openCP(uint256).details: Open collateral position and generate tokens

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions anymore. Can only be called by the current owner.     * > Note: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby removing any functionality that is only available to the owner.

transfer(address,uint256).details: Transfer collateral position to new user

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.

updateRate(uint256).details: Updates the rate for a peg to 1 USD based on the oracle contract.

withdrawETHCP(uint256,uint256).details: Witdraw ETH from existing CP || close CP when all of ETH is withdrawn

withdrawTokenCP(uint256,uint256).details: Mint new tokens from existing CP
